  "prompt": "What is the best HD led TV under 20000 rupees?",
  "response": "As of the latest information available, there are several good options for HD LED TVs under 20,000 INR. Keep in mind that prices and availability can vary, so it's wise to check the most recent reviews and deals. Here are some options that are often recommended in this price range:\n\n1. **Xiaomi Mi TV 4A** - Known for offering solid performance and features at a competitive price, Xiaomi's Mi TV 4A series has models that include smart TV functions, good picture quality, and a user-friendly interface.\n\n2. **Realme Smart TV** - Realme offers LED smart TVs with good picture quality and a smooth user experience thanks to Android TV OS integration.\n\n3. **OnePlus Y Series** - The OnePlus Y Series offers a good balance of picture quality and smart features, often at an attractive price point.\n\n4. **Samsung Wondertainment Series** - Samsung offers HD Ready models with good reliability and all-round performance in the Wondertainment series.\n\n5. **LG HD Ready LED TV** - LG is known for its high-quality panels and decent sound systems.\n\n6. **Sony Bravia Series** - While generally more expensive, sometimes basic models from Sony Bravia Series come close to this price range due to deals and discounts, offering excellent picture quality and sound.\n\n7. **TCL LED TV** - TCL has been providing affordable televisions with good smart features and a decent display quality.\n\nAlways check for the latest model specifications, customer reviews, and after-sales service in your area. Also, if you are interested in smart TV features, ensure the TV supports them to avoid needing an additional smart device like a Chromecast or Fire Stick.",
